Rep. Miller, Rep. Garrett Discuss Mortgage Notes: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-22T14:20:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/rep-miller-rep-garrett-discuss-mortgage-notes-audio.html
Representative Brad Miller, a North
Carolina Democrat, and Republican Representative  Scott Garrett  
of  New Jersey , say they are concerned about possible conflicts 
of interest involving holders of first and second mortgage 
notes. Miller and Garrett talk with Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt on 
Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."  They are joined by 
 Joshua Rosner  of Graham Fisher.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:38
 